  "body": "Geth should have a feature (i.e. cli flag) that will restrict the amount of inbound syncing peers that the node will serve data to. This should be an option to effectively be able to connect to lots of peers on Geth, but reducing network out bandwidth. Useful if the node is hosted on a hosting provider (such as AWS) that charges additional funds for outbound data.",
